.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Color: blue, green, red, white, yellow
Nationality: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
Beverage: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
Cigar: bluemaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
Music-Genre: electronic, blues, d&b, country, house
1. Nationality:british == Color:red
2. Nationality:swedish == Music-Genre:d&b
3. Nationality:danish == Beverage:tea
4. Color:green is on the left of Color:white
5. Color:green == Beverage:coffee
6. Cigar:pall-mall == Music-Genre:blues
7. Color:yellow == Cigar:dunhill
8. Beverage:milk is in the middle
9. Nationality:norwegian is on the far left
10. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Music-Genre:electronic
11. Music-Genre:houses is on the left or right of Cigar:dunhill
12. Cigar:bluemaster == Beverage:beer
13. Nationality:german == Cigar:prince
14. Nationality:norwegian is on the left or right of Color:blue
15. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Beverage:water

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    yellow	|     blue	|      red	|     green	|     white	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    danish	|    british	|    german	|    swedish	|
| Music-Genre		|     electronic	|    house	|     blues	|     country	|      d&b	|
| Beverage	|    water	|     tea	|     milk	|    coffee	|      beer	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   bluemaster	|
